  "cscw_dialogue": [
    {
      "turn_id": 1,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "我们需要画一下Atlas的组织结构。最顶层是Organization，一个组织下面可以有很多项目，然后每个项目里又包含集群和团队。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "ATLAS-ORGANIZATION",
        "ATLAS-PROJECTS",
        "MONGODB-CLUSTERS",
        "ATLAS-TEAMS"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白了，所以是三层结构：Organization → Projects → 下层元素。我想确认一下，集群和团队是并列挂在项目下面吗？还是团队管理集群这种关系？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "ATLAS-PROJECTS",
        "MONGODB-CLUSTERS",
        "ATLAS-TEAMS"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "对，是并列关系。团队和集群都是直接属于项目的，团队负责权限管理，集群是实际的数据库资源。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "ATLAS-PROJECTS",
        "MONGODB-CLUSTERS",
        "ATLAS-TEAMS"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，我先画出Organization到Projects的一对多关系，然后Projects分别连到Clusters和Teams。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "ATLAS-ORGANIZATION",
        "ATLAS-PROJECTS",
        "MONGODB-CLUSTERS",
        "ATLAS-TEAMS"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "等等，Organization和Projects之间应该是\"一个组织有多个项目\"，但反过来说，每个项目只能属于一个组织对吧？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "ATLAS-ORGANIZATION",
        "ATLAS-PROJECTS"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "是的，所以是一对多，Organization这边是单数，Projects那边是多。Projects到Clusters和Teams也是同样的逻辑。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "ATLAS-ORGANIZATION",
        "ATLAS-PROJECTS",
        "MONGODB-CLUSTERS",
        "ATLAS-TEAMS"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 7,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "没问题，这样结构就清晰了。标注关系的时候用\"has many\"来描述这种包含关系。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "ATLAS-ORGANIZATION",
        "ATLAS-PROJECTS",
        "MONGODB-CLUSTERS",
        "ATLAS-TEAMS"
